author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
It's exactly one week since "Back To The Beginning" in Birmingham - Ozzy Osbourne and Black Sabbath's last ever live show. Among the many covers was Jack Black's "Mr Crowley" tribute accompanied by a new generation of musicians - real ones. This is a longer episode because watching them encouraged my inner guitar nerd to come out and play. I've apologised. 

To watch Mr Crowley in its entirety: https://youtu.be/hm-M8GvgYws?si=qap23a4-shvUT0gj

And the original is here:  https://youtu.be/G3LvhdFEOqs?si=3AsUfwiscM99OKWz

To come and see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, find tickets here:

title: Why A Tribute to Ozzy & Randy Rhoads Inspired A Guitar Nerd....
